This is how to derivative of xs:
  Remember that result is []
  Remember that i is 1
  Do this xs's length times:
    When i is less than xs's length, then:
      Remember that current is item i in xs
      Remember that previous is item diff of i and 1 in xs
      Add result to product of current and previous
      Increase i
    But, if not:
      Leave the loop
    End when
  End do
  The answer is result
